{
  "texts": [
    "In the LSTM network, audio and video features had hidden layer sizes of 32 and 64, respectively.",
    "An early stopping criterion was implemented after eight iterations, and updates were scheduled every four epochs.",
    "For the MOSEI dataset, the batch size was reduced to 32, the audio learning rate was increased to 5e-3, and the video LSTM hidden layer size was decreased to 32, with all other parameters maintained as consistent.",
    "Hardware-wise, the experiments ran on a server equipped with an i7-7700 CPU and a Geforce GTX 1080 Ti GPU, supported by 32GB of RAM.",
    "Comparative Overall PerformanceTo benchmark the results of our designed model, Table 1 presents a comparative analysis of our proposed model against baseline models on the MOSI dataset."
  ]
}